Harmony Gold Shuts Unisel Mine After Worker Dies in Locomotive Accident

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-08T05:17:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/harmony-gold-shuts-unisel-mine-after-worker-dies-in-locomotive-accident.html
Harmony Gold Mining Co. said a worker
died yesterday in a locomotive accident at its Unisel mine in
 South Africa . The mine has been closed until all investigations
into the accident have been completed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  